"you can ¬ß7 an assumption of the form ¬ß6 to the goal ¬ß8.\n"
"\n"
"Other useful tactics for dealing with negation include: \n"
"* ¬ß3\n"
"* ¬ß4\n"
"* ¬ß5"

#. ¬ß0: `succ : ‚Ąē ‚Üí ‚Ąē`
