#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"An assumption of the form\n"
"¬ß0\n"
"can be decomposed, using ¬ß1, into the components ¬ß2 and ¬ß3.\n"
"\n"
"More generally, you can use ¬ß4 to select elements using the choice axiom:\n"
