#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic ¬ß0 adds the assumption ¬ß1 as an implication premise to the proof "
"goal:\n"
"from ¬ß2 and ¬ß3, we get ¬ß4.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"The tactic ¬ß5 does the exact opposite of ¬ß6."
