"The tactic ¬ß0 adds assumption ¬ß1 as an implication premise to the goal: \n"
"¬ß2 and ¬ß3 become ¬ß4. \n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relations\n"
"\n"
"The tactic ¬ß5 does the exact opposite of ¬ß6."

#. ¬ß0: `by_cases h : P`
