#. ¬ß6: `(h : ¬¨P)`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"The tactic ¬ß0 begins a case distinction as to whether ¬ß1 is true or false.\n"
"For example, ¬ß2 distinguishes between the cases ¬ß3 and ¬ß4.\n"
"\n"
"The proof goal is duplicated for this purpose, and\n"
"the assumption ¬ß5 is added to the first ‚Äúcopy,‚ÄĚ\n"
"while the assumption ¬ß6 is added to the second ‚Äúcopy.‚ÄĚ"
msgstr ""
"The tactic ¬ß0 distinguishes between the case where ¬ß1 is true and the case "
"where ¬ß1 is false. For example, ¬ß2 distinguishes between the cases ¬ß3 and "
"¬ß4. \n"
"\n"
"The goal is duplicated for this purpose, and assumption ¬ß5 is added to the "
"first ‚Äúcopy‚ÄĚ, while assumption ¬ß6 is added to the second ‚Äúcopy‚ÄĚ."

#. ¬ß0: `linarith`
#. ¬ß1: ```
#. h : m ‚Č§ x ‚Üí n < x
#. ```
