"(Technically, these are all lemmas in ¬ß1 that are marked with ¬ß2.)\n"
"\n"
"## Variants\n"
"\n"
"* ¬ß3 additionally uses the assumption ¬ß4 or the lemma ¬ß5 for simplification\n"
"* ¬ß6 additionally uses the definition of ¬ß7\n"
"* ¬ß8 exclusively uses the assumptions/lemmas/definitions ¬ß9, ¬ß10, and ¬ß11\n"
