"* ¬ß6 additionally uses the definition of ¬ß7 \n"
"* ¬ß8 exclusively uses the prerequisites/lemmas/definitions ¬ß9, ¬ß10 and ¬ß11 \n"
"* ¬ß12 shows you which lemmas were used"

#. ¬ß0: `constructor`
