"| ¬ß1 | ¬ß2 and ¬ß3 | \n"
"| ¬ß4 | ¬ß5 and ¬ß6 | \n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relations \n"
"\n"
"* You break down an *assumption* into its components using ¬ß7. \n"
"* If you want to prove ¬ß8, you must choose a side using ¬ß9 or ¬ß10."

