msgid ""
"The ¬ß0 tactic proves equations with the operations ¬ß1 in semirings,\n"
"in particular in ‚Ąē, ‚Ą§, ‚Ąö, ‚ĄĚ, ‚Ä¶   It works particularly well in commutative "
