"\n"
"| before | after | \n"
"|:------------ |:-------------|\n"
"| ¬ß1 | ¬ß2 | \n"
"| ¬ß3 | ¬ß4 | \n"
"\n"
"In nested expressions, it pushes the negation ¬ß5 as far to the right as "
"possible. For example, the goal \n"
"¬ß6\n"
"becomes \n"
"¬ß8\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relations \n"
"\n"
"The tactic is based on the two lemmas ¬ß9 and ¬ß10, which can be applied "
"individually with ¬ß11."

#. ¬ß0: ```
#. f = g
#. ```
