#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"Two mappings with the same range and domain are equal if\n"
"they take the same values on all elements of the domain.\n"
"A proof goal of the form\n"
"¬ß0\n"
"for mappings ¬ß1 is converted by ¬ß2\n"
"into the equation\n"
"¬ß3."
msgstr ""
"Two maps with the same range and the same domain are equal if they take the "
"same values on all elements of the domain. The tactic ¬ß2 transform a goal of "
"the form \n"
"¬ß0\n"
"for maps ¬ß1 into a goal of the form\n"
"¬ß3."

#. ¬ß0: ```
