#: Game.Levels.Implis.L03_Apply
msgid "This should seem obvious now"
msgstr "**You**: Yes, that seems natural to me now, too."

#. ¬ß0: `apply hAB at h`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L03_Apply
msgid "Us the given implication by trying ¬ß0"
msgstr ""
