#. ¬ß0: $A \\Rightarrow B \\Rightarrow C$
#. ¬ß1: $A \\Rightarrow C$
#. ¬ß2: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Combine implications ¬ß0 into ¬ß1. Try ¬ß2"
msgstr ""
"**You**: I'm supposed to combine implications ¬ß0 to ¬ß1? \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: Perhaps you should start with ¬ß2 again?"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Conclusion Implis L04"
msgstr "**Head of Operations**: You guys are really great!"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Intro Implis L04"
msgstr "**Head of Operations**: Here's another local problem."

#. ¬ß0: `¬ę{hB}¬Ľ : ¬ę{B}¬Ľ`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Now assumption ¬ß0 is available"
msgstr ""
"**Scribble**: ‚Ä¶ and, having done that, you have ¬ß0 available as an "
"assumption."

#. ¬ß0: `B`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Prove ¬ß0"
msgstr "**Scribble**: Now you can first prove ¬ß0 ‚Ä¶"

#. ¬ß0: `have hB : B`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L04_Apply
msgid "Try holding onto ¬ß0"
msgstr ""
"**Head of Operations**: Well, *I* would explicitly spell out ¬ß0 at this "
"point. \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: A bit verbose for my taste. But okay, we can do that. \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble** *(to you)*: Go on, give it a try!"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "Conclusion Implis L05"
msgstr ""
"The Head of Operations once again expresses his gratitude. He presses a few "
"more buttons, and with a loud rattling noise, several conveyor belts start "
