msgstr ""
"**You**: So, I need to find a path of implications ¬ß0. \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: Let me guess how we start ‚Ä¶ ¬ß1 again?"

#. ¬ß0: `apply`
#: Game.Levels.Implis.L05_Apply
msgid "Hier again use ¬ß0"
msgstr "**Scribble**: Well, ¬ß0 again. What else?"

#. ¬ß0: $$
#.   \\begin{CD}
#.        A  @>{f}>> B @<{g}<< C    \\ %(new line)
#.     @V{h}VV    @V{i}VV   @V{j}VV \\ %(new line)
