msgstr ""
"**You**: Well, I could at least start with ¬ß0 ‚Ä¶ \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: ‚Ä¶ then we'll take it from there!"

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L10_Iff
msgid "Conclusion Implis L10"
msgstr ""
"**Head of Operations**: Okay, great. That should work. \n"
"\n"
"He's on the phone again. \n"
"\n"
"**Head of Operations**: Bingo!"

#. ¬ß0: `rw`
