msgstr "The tactics ¬ß0 and ¬ß1 can often be used in place of this statement."

#: Game.Levels.Implis.L14_Summary
msgid "Conclusion Implis L14"
msgstr ""
"**Head of Operations**: That's fantastic! Thank you so much! Then I won't "
"keep you any longer. I'm sure you want to continue to the planet Quantus, "
"right? \n"
"\n"
"**You**: Um, maybe ‚Ä¶ \n"
"\n"
"**Head of Operations**: I would just like to ask for one more favour. I have "
"a package here for the Queen of Quantus! It was also left to me by my "
"predecessor. Formal Mail won't accept it because I don't know the address. "
"Could you perhaps take it to her? \n"
"\n"
"**You**: Sure! Scribble, can you take it? \n"
"\n"
"Scribble takes and swallows the parcel.  The Head of Operations looks at him "
"in disbelief. \n"
"\n"
"**Robo**: Don't worry, I don't digest anything!"

#. ¬ß0: `‚Üí`
