#: Game.Levels.Mono
msgid "Intro Mono"
msgstr ""
"On the next planet, there are again two skyscrapers standing next to each "
"other. Again, one is narrow and tall, the other slightly wider and shorter. "
"And once again, they are connected by a system of tubes ‚Äď there appears to "
"be some kind of transport capsule system again. \n"
"\n"
"After your experience on Epo, you head straight for the shorter skyscraper "
"this time and land on the roof. \n"
"\n"
"**Porter**:  No, no, no. Didn't you see everyone waving? These are just our "
"sleeping quarters. During the day, we're always over there, in the office "
"tower. Anyway, now that you're here ‚Äď welcome! \n"
"\n"
"You each shake one of his four hands. \n"
"\n"
"**Porter**: At least this gives me the opportunity to introduce you to our "
"unique local transport system. You're from Epo, aren't you? We hear terrible "
"stories from there. There's an accident every other day. They just can't get "
"their tubes sorted out. We've been accident-free for years! \n"
"\n"
"You go down four floors. There, everyone is assigned a capsule again, and "
"you glide silently uphill into the office tower. How the capsule operates "
"remains a mystery.\n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: Oh. There's no one here either! \n"
"\n"
"**Porter**: Of course not. They're all upstairs, top floor. And not every "
"floor can be reached via a tube. But we're almost there. Just two more "
"flights of stairs."

