"magnificent? Let's go up!\n"
"\n"
"**You** *(to Scribble)*: Let's try to formulate the statement we want to "
"show to Guino. There is exactly one even ‚Ä¶ \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: Hold on! We haven't come across any unique existence "
"statements so far."

