"**Scribble**: While we're waiting, I'll quickly show you how negation works "
"with quantifiers. I have a feeling we'll need this in a moment."

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
msgid "Conclusion Quantus L09"
msgstr ""
"The formalosophers are enthusiastic. Once the applause has died down, you "
"have a question. \n"
"\n"
"**You**: I have to stay we still feel a bit lost in the Leaniverse.  Could "
"anyone here give us some directions?\n"
"\n"
"**All**: Yes, yes. \n"
"\n"
"**You**: Who? \n"
"\n"
"That question was too specific again. Awkward silence."

#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
msgid "Intro Quantus L09"
msgstr ""
"After much back and forth, the formalosophers have finally agreed on the "
"following question."

#. ¬ß0: `not_odd_iff_even`
#: Game.Levels.Quantus.L09_PushNeg
