"¬ß4 (¬ß5 is odd), ¬ß6, ¬ß7 (solves equations containing ¬ß8), ¬ß9,\n"
"¬ß10, ¬ß11 (to tackle ¬ß12 in goal), ¬ß13 (to disect ¬ß14 in assumptions),\n"
