msgstr ""
"**You**: I understand. But now I've really had enough of this predicate "
"nonsense! \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: Then we'd better fly on! But in case you're interested ‚Äď "
"here's an overview over the key lessons from this planet.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"| notation  | meaning | \n"
"|:--------------|:----------------------------| \n"
