msgid "Intro Samarkand L08"
msgstr "**Arapuka**: Could you perhaps even help me with this conjecture?"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn
msgid "Intro Saturn"
msgstr ""
"You never actually want to approach this planet. But you weren't entirely as "
"focussed as one needs to be in an universe, especially in a universe one is "
"not entirely familiar with. Now you're already too close, the gravity is too "
"strong, and your regenerative power unit is currently in regeneration mode.\n"
"\n"
"**You**: What is this orange sauce on the planet?\n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: It looks rather toxic. Or hot.\n"
"\n"
"**You**: Or both. I really don't want to land there! \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: Neither do I. I'm trying my best not to. And look how much "
"rubbish is already orbiting here! The best we can do right now is fly with "
"the current."

#: Game.Levels.Saturn
msgid "Saturn"
msgstr "Saturn"

#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L01_Rewrite_equality
msgid "Conclusion Saturn L01"
msgstr "You receive a ūüĎć."

