msgstr ""
"**You**: How does that work again with rewriting backwards? \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: ¬ß2, where you write ¬ß0 as ¬ß1."

#. ¬ß0: `rw [h‚āď]`
#. ¬ß1: `rw [‚Üź h‚āď]`
