msgid "Try if ¬ß0 and ¬ß1 can be used as in Implis"
msgstr ""
"**You**: So I can also use ¬ß0 and ¬ß1? \n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: Why don't you try?"

#. ¬ß0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Saturn.L02_Ring_add_pow_two
msgid "Conclusion Saturn L02: ¬ß0 could have been used as well"
msgstr ""
"You receive a ūüĎć.\n"
"\n"
"**Scribble**: You could have just said ¬ß0, though."

