"need to remember to precede them with a space ‚Äď like this: ¬ß5.\n"
"\n"
"**You**: Okay, I'll keep that in mind. But given that this map only takes "
"values in ‚Ąē, there's nothing to be proven here. \n"

#: Game.Levels.Vieta.L01_FunctionNotation
msgid "Intro Vieta L01"
msgstr ""
"**Vieta:** Listen, I'll show you something ‚Ä¶ He gives you a piece of paper."

#. ¬ß0: `fun (x : ‚Ą§) ‚Ü¶ x ^ 2`
#. ¬ß1: $x‚Ü¶x^2$
#. ¬ß2: `f : ‚Ą§ ‚Üí ‚Ą§ := ‚Ä¶`
#. ¬ß3: $$
#. \\begin{aligned}
#. f\\colon \\mathbb{‚Ą§} &\\to \\mathbb{‚Ą§} \\ %(new line)
#. x &\\mapsto x ^ 2
#. \\end{aligned}
#. $$
